        <p>Estaminet is a premium pilsner brewed by Palm Breweries. It features high-quality summer barley, Saaz hops, and a distinctive yeast. The beer undergoes slow, traditional bottom fermentation for six weeks, resulting in a fruity character and refreshing taste.</p>
